<section id="step-1" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 1</p>
      <p>Search for TeX Live on Google and visit the website.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-1.png" alt="Google search for TeX Live"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-2" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 2</p>
      <p>Download the installation file for your operating system.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-2.png" alt="TeX Live download page"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-3" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 3</p>
      <p>Run the TeX Live Installer. On Windows, your account name must be in English.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="figure-stack">
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-3-1.png" alt="TeX Live installer"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-3-2.png" alt="TeX Live installer running"></figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-4" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 4</p>
      <p>After a short wait, click <strong>Advanced</strong>.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-4.png" alt="Advanced button"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-5" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 5</p>
      <p>In <strong>Selections</strong>, click <strong>Change</strong> and select <strong>small scheme</strong>.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-5.png" alt="Selecting small scheme"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-6" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 6</p>
      <p>Click <strong>Customize</strong> and select your preferred language.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-6.png" alt="Selecting language"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-7" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 7</p>
      <p>Click <strong>Install</strong>. When the installation is complete, click <strong>Close</strong>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="figure-stack">
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-7.png" alt="Installation in progress"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-8.png" alt="Installation complete"></figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-8" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 8</p>
      <p>Run the TeX Live Manager.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-9.png" alt="TeX Live manager"></figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-9" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 9</p>
      <p>Select <strong>Not installed</strong>, search <strong>latexmk</strong>, select the two packages, then click <strong>install marked</strong>.</p>
      <p>To install additional packages in the future, repeat Steps 8 and 9.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="figure-stack">
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-10.png" alt="Searching for latexmk"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-11.png" alt="Selecting latexmk packages"></figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="error-path" class="callout-card">
  <p class="eyebrow">Troubleshooting</p>
  <h2>Error: PATH environment variable</h2>
  <p>Occasionally, Windows may show environment-variable-related errors during or after setup.</p>
  <div class="doc-section-grid" style="margin-top:1rem;">
    <ol>
      <li>Run View Advanced System Settings.</li>
      <li>Click Environment Variables.</li>
      <li>Under System Variables, click Path and then Edit.</li>
      <li>Click New.</li>
      <li>Enter the <code>%ComSpec%</code> path value.</li>
      <li>Click OK.</li>
    </ol>
    <div class="figure-stack">
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-12.png" alt="PATH setup 1"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-13-1.png" alt="PATH setup 2"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-13-2.png" alt="PATH setup 3"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-13-3.png" alt="PATH setup 4"></figure>
      <figure class="image-frame"><img src="/assets/images/1.1-13-4.png" alt="PATH setup 5"></figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
